description:
On today’s show, Emily is taking your calls to give you the hacks that will elevate your relationships and your oral game.

She discusses the surprising lessons short term relationships can teach us, a new oral sex method you’ll definitely to want to try, and how to teach your partner a new kissing style. Plus, she cracks down on the signs you may or may not be ready to move in with your partner.
